<plot>Salvator Cangemi (Antonio Sabato) is a produce purveyor in Milan, Italy whom moonlights as a pimp and runs a profitable twin businesses. But the appearance of a ruthless and greedy French gangster called Le Capitaine (Philippe Leroy) threatens Toto's livelihood when Le Capitaine wants to unite the organized crime in Milian for him getting a large share of the profits. But Toto wants no part of Le Capitaine's organization and wants to continue running his own ring in a low-key quiet way. But no one says "no" to Le Capitaine and he threatens an all-out war to keep his organized crime ring, and reputation, intact.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?369797</url></doc>
